premise_source_doc_sentence: Mariqueen Maandig Reznor  (  née Maandig ; born April 5 , 1981  )  is a Filipino American musician and singer-songwriter .
She is best known as the vocalist for How to Destroy Angels , and was the former vocalist of Los Angeles-based rock band West Indian Girl .
